milestones.description: Josh Davey has taken the most five-wicket hauls (2) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Gordon Goudie's record
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Calum MacLeod has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Hamilton's record

stories.title: All-round Davey crushes Afghanistan
stories.subTitle: Dubai Triangular Series 2014-15
stories.summary: A six-wicket haul from the fast bowler Josh Davey helped bundle Afghanistan out for 63 and set up Scotland's 150-run win in Abu Dhabi
